709675f-a.title: Manhattan: 7th Avenue - 16th Street (West)
709675f-a.text:
116 to 100 Seventh Ave., west side, south from West 17th to 16th
Streets, showing prominently a 12-story loft building, bearing No. 110-
106 Seventh Ave. and No. 206 West 17th Street. Partially shown on the
extreme right is No. 118 Seventh Ave., a 5-story structure at the N.W.
corner of West 17th Street.
October 1911.
Gift of E.M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
